#Yurlok (#1085) generic-payment witness - PARKED, engine-blocked. With pool
#exactly {B}{R}{G} (from Yurlok's add), a hill giant ({2}{R}) will not cast:
#the click is consumed, the spell never stacks, all 3 mana float. Exact-color
#spends from the same pool work (the committed test's shock). Driving the
#payment with choice clicks HANGS the suite (a half-open payment menu).
#Mechanism: generic costs paid from COLORED-ONLY pools - prior passing tests
#always had colorless objects for the generic part (blitz pool {3}{G}{R}).
#Engine fuel: auto-payment color selection for generic costs.
[INIT]
firstmain
[PLAYER1]
manapool:{1}
inplay:497813
hand:hill giant
[PLAYER2]
[DO]
497813
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
hill giant
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
[ASSERT]
FIRSTMAIN
[PLAYER1]
inplay:497813,hill giant
manapool:{B}{G}
tappedinplay:1
[PLAYER2]
manapool:{B}{R}{G}
[END]
